General Information

This is a high protein, high fat, low carbohydrate ketogenic shake. Medium chain triglycerides from coconut oil are used in this shake to increase the saturated fat content which when combined with a ketogenic diet helps our body to burn fat as a fuel source as oppose to carbohydrate. It also contains protein which contributes to maintenance and development of lean muscle mass.

Common Uses

Post workout shake/keto friendly snack

Ingredients

Whey Protein Concentrate (milk), Coconut Oil Powder, Cocoa Powder (7%), Natural Flavourings, Xanthan Gum (thickener), Sucralose (sweetener).

Directions

Add 40g (4 scoops) to 400ml of water & shake well!
